reviewText: gorgeous! time waits for no one, Tom Waits for everyone - at least this fantastic release!
A truly great live performance! If you like Waits,dont miss this!!

Tom Waits performance was very humorous and sentimental at the same time!  The broadcast should have won an Emmy award.  I was in my late teens when I first viewed this performance on PBS.  He, Tom Waits can act well, as he did in the movie Seven Psychopaths.
The CD's of SXSW were not as clear as I would have liked but part of that could be Tom.  The VHI Storyteller was a bit more to my liking but overall, I was pleased.
This was not available for a long time, when it was it was more costly than i would have liked but is a good combination of music and video performance.

Great Set! This package is really worth the price. I paid no more than I would for an average new DVD, so both CD's is really a bonus. If you're a fan of the great Mr. Tom Waits, I think you'll watch this one over and over.
